<title>USA: U.S. HEADLINE STOCKS -- Issues to watch - April 1.</title>
<headline>U.S. HEADLINE STOCKS -- Issues to watch - April 1.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Stocks to watch this morning:</p>
<p>* Hillenbrand Industries Inc reported first quarter earnings per share of $0.56, up from $0.48 a year ago. The First Call estimate was $0.53.</p>
<p>* International Business Machines Corp shares were up 1/4 at 137-5/8 in London. Philip Morris Cos Inc was up 1/2 to 114-5/8.</p>
<p>* Trans World Airlines Inc said Monday it expected its first quarter operating loss to exceed the year-earlier operating loss. Shares closed at 6-15/16.</p>
